Title: Samsung Galaxy S20+ Diagnostic Service
Body (HTML):
Samsung Galaxy S20+ Diagnostic Service

 

At iFixYouri, we understand. Your Samsung Galaxy S20+ is really important to you. When it breaks, it can really mess up your day. If you are in need of Diagnostic Service, let the professional repair technicians at iFixYouri help you out.

 

*NOTE: If you decline repairs for diagnostic or water damage treatment or your device is deemed non-repairable, you will be responsible for shipping and handling.

This is the service you need if you aren't quite sure what the problem with your Samsung Galaxy S20+ is. We'll find out what is going on, and contact you with a repair quote.

 

Every repair service begins with a series of diagnostic tests to determine what the issue is. Our technicians use their repair experience to quickly diagnose the problem. In most cases, repairs are minimal; however, if we see that your Samsung Galaxy S20+ has additional damage, we'll contact you before proceeding.

 

Free UPS ground shipping and $100 of insurance are included. You may purchase faster shipping options and additional insurance protection using the drop-down options above. That's up to you. Don't send us your cables, charges, or cases please. We have plenty here already :) Just package your Samsung Galaxy S20+ in a secure box and affix the provided label.

 

Questions about Diagnostic Service? Type them into the box below, and we'll get back to you as soon as possible. Alternatively, you can reach us at 888-494-4349 or support@ifixyouri.com

Title: Samsung Galaxy S20+ Glass & LCD Repair
Body (HTML):
Samsung Galaxy S20+ Glass & LCD Repair

 

We recommend not trying Glass & LCD Repair yourself. Devices have become more and more sophisticated and you may cause more damage. Using the supplied shipping label, send your Samsung Galaxy S20+ to iFixYouri's mail-in center so our skilled repair technicians can inspect your device, pinpoint all/any issues affecting it, and get them repaired the professional way.

Those who have only cracked glass, NOT a broken LCD, should opt for our Samsung Galaxy S20+ Glass Repair. This service is for both cracked glass and a broken LCD.

 

After checkout, you'll receive an email confirmation and shipping label. When your phone arrives at our repair center, we do diagnostic tests to determine if any other issues are at play. Outgoing testing ensures that your Samsung Galaxy S20+ is fully functional. With the repairs complete, we send you a tracking number and ship your Samsung Galaxy S20+ back to you!

 

Send your Samsung Galaxy S20+ to iFixYouri via the UPS shipping method of your choosing. Please ship your device in a sturdy, secure box. If you hear it rattling around in the box, add some more padding. Please do not include cases, cables, or accessories. Standard UPS Ground is covered by us, as well as $100 insurance. Faster shipping and extra insurance coverage can be purchased using the drop-down boxes above.

 

A 90-day warranty that covers all but accidental damage is included. Contact customer service with any questions at 888-494-4349 or support@ifixyouri.com.

 

iFixYouri can be reached at 888-494-4349 or support@ifixyouri.com. Get your Samsung Galaxy S20+ working like new with the help of experienced technicians who do the job right the first time, and save yourself a lot of money and hassle.

Title: Samsung Galaxy S20+ Battery Replacement
Body (HTML):
Samsung Galaxy S20+ Battery Replacement

 

The Samsung Galaxy S20+ has great build quality and design, but it isn't invincible. Since your device is of little use when broken, it's a good idea to bring it to iFixYouri for expert Battery Replacement.

 

Each device has its own lifespan - some devices use higher quality components than others and can last years if properly maintained. Drops, water or liquid, even a jolt can damage your device.

Old or bad batteries can really be frustrating. You might need Battery Replacement if your battery does not hold charge well or charges very slowly or barely at all.

 

With Battery Replacement for Samsung Galaxy S20+, iFixYouri is here to help. With this service, our repair technicians inspect the problem, as well as any other affected components, repair your device, and send it back to you asap. If there are any other issues affecting your device, we'll let you know and proceed with those repairs only after your approval.

 

We email you a printable shipping label, and include $100 of insurance protection. If you would like faster shipping or more insurance coverage, you have the option to upgrade above using the drop-downs.

 

All replacement parts come with a 90-day warranty that covers all but accidental damage.

 

Do you have any questions about Battery Replacement from iFixYouri? Just ask them in the box below, and we'll get back to you. Alternatively, you can always reach us via our support phone number 888-494-4349 or email support@ifixyouri.com
